textObjects.text: INVASION As the battle-weary heroes recuperate and repair their gear, Spider-Man makes make a discovery that will change his life and his costume!
As awesome and striking as Spider-Man’s new black costume is, you can’t help but stare at the crazy super-brawl taking place behind Spidey. Artist Mike Zeck nailed this cover, without a doubt.
